Ed Miliband 's son has inadvertently waded into the row about the Labour leader 's kitchen as he declared it ` the best ' in his house .
The unwitting admission from five-year-old Daniel Daniel , came as Mr Miliband yet again wheeled out his children for the cameras .
It is the fourth time they have appeared on screen during the campaign .
Mr Miliband was forced to admit he needs two kitchens .